Op TENNANT III.event desc: Liberation Malden continues... not long now before OP RELIC II!

CIC Phase 1.event desc: Phase 1 of the Combat Infantry Courses covers the basic techniques and SOPs thag are required to attend operations. Topics covered include Weapons Handling and the 6 Section Battle Drills, combining theory with practical exercises against targets and live enemy. Recruits are required to attend this; trained members are welcome to assist.
